            <br />
            <p>@sharedLocalizer["[Company Placeholder] does not warrant that functions contained in this site’s content will be uninterrupted or error free, that defects will be corrected, or that the site or the server that makes it available are free of viruses or bugs."]</p>

            <h2 class="page-title">@sharedLocalizer["Downloads"]</h2>
            <p>@sharedLocalizer["Every care is taken to ensure any files available for download from this site are free from viruses. However, [Company Placeholder] except no liability for the following losses or damage caused as a result of downloading files from this site: (a) loss of data; (b) loss of revenue or anticipated profits; (c) loss of business; (d) loss of opportunity; (e) loss of goodwill or injury to reputation; (f) losses suffered by third parties; or (g) any indirect, consequential, special or exemplary damages arising from the use of this site regardless of the form of action."]</p>

            <h2 class="page-title">@sharedLocalizer["Intellectual Property"]</h2>
            <p>@sharedLocalizer["The names, images and logos identifying [Company Placeholder] and their products and services are subject to copyright."]</p>

            <h2 class="page-title">@sharedLocalizer["Complaints"]</h2>
            <p>@sharedLocalizer["You can complain to the support helpdesk on [Company Placeholder Email], then to the managing director on [Company Placeholder Escalation Email] and we will respond within 5 working days."]</p>

            <h2 class="page-title">@sharedLocalizer["As a Nominet registrar"]</h2>
            <p>@sharedLocalizer["When a request is made for the registering of a new domain, or when advising our clients about upcoming domain renewals by email, we explain our key terms and how we operate by means of email. Other key terms include:"]</p>
            <br />
            <ul>
                <li>@sharedLocalizer["What we charge for the domain-name related service we provide;"]</li>
                <li>@sharedLocalizer["Our cancellation policy and how you can renew a domain name and the basis on which you will be charged for maintaining the registration of a domain name;"]</li>
