                <li>@sharedLocalizer["If you would like to report an issue with one of the domains on our tag relating to spam, phishing, malware, etc. please send an email to our support team."]</li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <p>@sharedLocalizer["Nominet is the central registry for .uk domains. When you register a .uk domain with us you also enter into a contract with Nominet, the terms of which can be found"] <a href="http://www.nominet.org.uk/uk-domain-names/registering-uk-domain/legal-details/terms-and-conditions-domain-name-registration">@sharedLocalizer["here"]</a>.</p>

